node.text: Last year inside Dickies Arena, Jose Vitor Leme, Kaique Pacheco, and Cooper Davis walked away with first, second, and third. Fast forward to 2021, and the three World Champions are in the same order going into the Iron Cowboy. It will be a race to the finish line again in Fort Worth, TX. 📺: @cbssports Network 8 P.M. ET.
